values.title: Interactive page building experience for Nuxt
values.lead: Simple content pages or complex landing pages. The Blokkli editor provides a solid modular framework to build your own editing experience - with any backend.

values.text: Blokkli is just the editor. It does not manage content for you, it does not provide any blocks, forms or richt text editing.
What it does offer is a modular framework that makes it possible to integrate Blokkli in any existing or new setup built using NuxtJS.

What it does offer is a modular framework that makes it possible to integrate Blokkli in any existing or new setup built using NuxtJS. Via the simple adapter interface you can connect any data source (CMS or any backend).
This means that Blokkli isn't a "install and forget" library: It requires manual work to connect your data source, setup the adapter. But once that's done, adding new block types is a breeze.
